This is how to solve of N:
  Remember that answer is ""
  Remember that started is no
  Remember that power is 1
  Do this N times:
    When product of power and 2 is at most N, then:
      Remember that power is product of power and 2
    But, if not:
      Leave the loop
    End when
  End do
  Do this N times:
    When power is more than 0, then:
      When power is at least N, then:
        Remember that answer is "{answer}1"
        Remember that N is diff of N and power
        Remember that started is yes
      But, if not:
        When started is yes, then:
          Remember that answer is "{answer}0"
        End when
      End when
      Remember that power is quotient of power and 2
    But, if not:
      Leave the loop
    End when
  End do
  The answer is answer
